tioned in 1295.\n\n==Geography==\nThe [[municipality]] lies at an [[altitude]] of 331 metres and covers an [[area]] of 5.785&nbsp;km\u00b2. It has a [[population]] of about 795 people.\n\n==Notable people==\n[[Hungary|Hungarian]] politician [[J\u00e1nos Gy\u00f6ngy\u00f6si]], who served as [[Minister of Foreign Affairs]] between 1944 and 1947.\n\n==External links==\n\n{{Presov District}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rokycany, Presov District}}\n[[Category:Villages and municipalities in Pre\u0161ov District]]\n[[Category:\u0160ari\u0161]]\n\n{{Pre\u0161ov-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rokycany,_Pre%C5%A1ov_District"}
{"title_page": "Rokycany District", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name                   = Rokycany District\n|other_name             =\n|native_name            = Okres Rokycany\n|nickname               = \n|settlement_type        = [[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|motto                  =\n<!-- images and maps  ----------->\n|image_skyline          = Rokycany CZ Our Lady of the Snow church and Marian column 0589.jpg\n|imagesize              = 300px\n|image_caption          = [[Rokycany]] town\n|image_map              = Map CZ - district Rokycany.PNG\n|mapsize                = 300px\n|map_caption            = District location in the [[Plze\u0148 Region]] within the [[Czech Republic]]\n|image_map1             = Rokycany District 2010 names RO CZ.png\n|mapsize1               = 300px\n|map_caption1           = Municipalities of Rokycany District\n<!-- Location ------------------>\n|subdivision_type       = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n|subdivision_name       = [[Czech Republic]]\n|subdivision_type1      = [[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1      = [[Plze\u0148 Region|Plze\u0148]]\n|subdivision_type2      = Capital\n|subdivision_name2      = [[Rokycany]]\n|subdivision_type3      = \n|subdivision_name3      =\n<!-- Politics ----------------->\n|government_footnotes   =\n|government_type        =\n|leader_title           =\n|leader_name            =\n|established_title      =\n|established_date       = \n<!-- Area    --------------------->\n|area_magnitude         = \n|unit_pref              =\n|area_footnotes         =\n|area_total_km2         = 575.11\n|area_land_km2          =\n|area_metro_km2         =\n<!-- Population   ----------------------->\n|population_as_of       = 2019-01-01<ref>{{cite web |title=Population of municipalities of the Czech republic|url=https://www.czso.cz/documents/10180/91917344/1300721903.pdf/ea01e710-2ae5-49f3-8792-ebb384754346?version=1.0|publisher=Czech Statistical Office|accessdate=201